nuclear /ˈnjuːklɪə/

1. ADJ Nuclear means relating to the nuclei of atoms, or to the energy released when these nuclei are split or combined. 核的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...a nuclear power station. …一座核电站。 

例： ...nuclear energy. …核能。 

2. ADJ Nuclear means relating to weapons that explode by using the energy released when the nuclei of atoms are split or combined. 核武器的 [ADJ n] 

例： They rejected a demand for the removal of all nuclear weapons. 他们拒绝了清除所有核武器的要求。

